Pasta
20
Italian
image
Bacon, 100, grams
Spaghetti, 250, grams
Egg, 2, stk
Parmesan, 50, grams


Boil pasta in salted water
Cut bacon into small pieces and fry until crispy
Add egg, cheese and pepper to a bowl and mix
Drain pasta and add it to the bacon
Add egg and cheese mixture to the pasta and mix
Serve with parmesan on top

